---
// hero.astro — Synopsis / Diary section
// Sin <!DOCTYPE>, <html>, <head> ni <body> — eso lo maneja Layout.astro
---

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gloria+Hallelujah&family=VT323&family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

<section class="diary-section">

  <div class="sticker sticker--star-tl"       aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono1.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--butterfly-tr"  aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono2.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--heart-bl"      aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono3.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--star-br"       aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono6.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--glitter-1"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono5.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--glitter-2"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono6.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--butterfly-2"   aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono7.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--star-tl-2"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono7.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--butterfly-tr-2" aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono6.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--heart-bl-2"    aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono5.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--star-br-2"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono4.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--glitter-3"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono3.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--glitter-4"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono2.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--butterfly-3"   aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono1.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--star-tl-3"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono1.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--heart-bl-3"    aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono6.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--star-br-3"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono4.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--butterfly-4"   aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono5.png" alt="" /></div>
  <div class="sticker sticker--glitter-5"     aria-hidden="true"><img src="/icono7.png" alt="" /></div>

  <div class="tape tape--tl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="tape tape--tr" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="diary-page">
    <div class="diary-header">
      <span class="diary-date">Tuesday, October 31, 2004</span>
      <div class="diary-doodles" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>♥</span><span>☆</span><span>♥</span><span>☆</span><span>♥</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="diary-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="diary-body">
      <aside class="margin-note margin-note--left" aria-label="Nota al margen">
        <span>☆ super</span><span>girl</span><span>☆</span><span class="margin-arrow">→</span>
      </aside>

      <div class="diary-text">
        <p class="diary-entry diary-entry--1">
          <span class="diary-cap">H</span>ello diary!. Today I am
          <span class="underline-pink">SUPER</span> angry with Leo.
          Again. In case you don't remember, he's my little brother, the most
          <span class="scribble-word">annoying</span> person in the entire universe,
          and he's been <em>touching my things</em> again. I told Mum not to
          let him into my room, but of course, as always, no one in this house
          cares what I say.
        </p>

        <div class="stain stain--coffee" tabindex="0" aria-label="Mancha en el diario">
          <span class="stain-hidden-msg">My doll is acting weird...</span>
        </div>

        <p class="diary-entry diary-entry--2">
          This time he moved <span class="highlight-pink">ALL</span> of the
          collectible doll mansion that Mum brought me from Paris. The limited edition,
          diary, the one that cost 400 euros! Miss Crystal was upside down.
          Miss Crystal is <span class="scribble-word scribble-word--angry">NEVER</span> upside down. He did it. I know it.
        </p>

        <p class="diary-entry diary-entry--3">
          But this time I have a <span class="underline-pink">PLAN</span>.
          Dad gave me the pink glittery mobile phone
          <span class="sticker-inline">pink phone</span>
          I've wanted for ages for my birthday. I'm going to take photos with it
          to send to Mum. That way I'll have <em>proof.</em>
          Leo won't get away with it this time.
        </p>

        <aside class="margin-note margin-note--right" aria-label="Nota al margen">
          <span>I love</span><span>Cristal</span><span class="margin-star">★</span>
        </aside>

        <p class="diary-entry diary-entry--4">
          Right. I've taken <span class="text-horror">14 photos.</span>
          In the first ones, everything is as usual. Normal. But from
          photo number seven onwards...
        </p>

        <div class="horror-divider" aria-hidden="true"><span>— — —</span></div>

        <p class="diary-entry diary-entry--5 diary-entry--horror">
          I'm scared, this isn't
          <span class="horror-word">normal...</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="glitch-text" data-text="Who's in my room?">Who's in my doll's house?</span>
        </p>

        <div class="diary-signature">
          <span class="signature-name">— Nerea</span>
          <div class="signature-doodles" aria-hidden="true">♥ ★ ♥</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="torn-edge torn-edge--bottom" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  :root {
    --pink-hot:      #FF69B4;
    --pink-neon:     #FF1493;
    --pink-pastel:   #FFB1D1;
    --pink-light:    #FFE4F0;
    --pink-paper:    #FFF0F7;
    --blood:         #8B0000;
    --blood-light:   #C0392B;
    --ink-dark:      #2C1A1A;
    --ink-blue:      #1A237E;
    --coffee:        #6F4E37;
    --white:         #FFFFFF;
    --font-diary:    'Gloria Hallelujah', cursive;
    --font-margin:   'VT323', monospace;
    --font-pixel:    'Press Start 2P', monospace;
  }

  .diary-section {
    position: relative; z-index: 30;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100vh; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; overflow: hidden;
  }

  .sticker {
    position: absolute; font-size: 1.8rem; pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none; z-index: 2;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 6px rgba(255,105,180,0.6));
    animation: sticker-float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .sticker img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }

  .sticker--star-tl        { top: 2rem;    left: 2rem;   width: 2rem;   height: 2rem; }
  .sticker--butterfly-tr   { top: 4rem;    right: 3rem;  width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .sticker--heart-bl       { bottom: 5rem; left: 4rem;   width: 2rem;   height: 2rem; animation-delay: 1.2s; }
  .sticker--star-br        { bottom: 8rem; right: 2rem;  width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .sticker--glitter-1      { top: 30%;     left: 1rem;   width: 1.8rem; height: 1.8rem; animation-delay: 0.9s; }
  .sticker--glitter-2      { top: 60%;     right: 1rem;  width: 1.6rem; height: 1.6rem; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .sticker--butterfly-2    { bottom: 20%;  left: 6rem;   width: 2rem;   height: 2rem; animation-delay: 2s; }
  .sticker--star-tl-2      { top: 8rem;    left: 5rem;   width: 2rem;   height: 2rem; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .sticker--butterfly-tr-2 { top: 10rem;   right: 6rem;  width: 2.2rem; height: 2.2rem; animation-delay: 1.2s; }
  .sticker--heart-bl-2     { bottom: 8rem; left: 7rem;   width: 2rem;   height: 2rem; animation-delay: 1.9s; }
  .sticker--star-br-2      { bottom: 7rem; right: 6rem;  width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .sticker--glitter-3      { top: 45%;     left: 3rem;   width: 1.6rem; height: 1.6rem; animation-delay: 2.5s; }
  .sticker--glitter-4      { top: 70%;     right: 4rem;  width: 1.5rem; height: 1.5rem; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .sticker--butterfly-3    { bottom: 40%;  left: 8rem;   width: 1.7rem; height: 1.7rem; animation-delay: 2.8s; }
  .sticker--star-tl-3      { top: 15rem;   left: 1rem;   width: 1.8rem; height: 1.8rem; animation-delay: 1.1s; }
  .sticker--heart-bl-3     { bottom: 15rem; left: 2rem;  width: 1.9rem; height: 1.9rem; animation-delay: 2.1s; }
  .sticker--star-br-3      { bottom: 12rem; right: 3rem; width: 2.2rem; height: 2.2rem; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .sticker--butterfly-4    { top: 55%;     right: 2rem;  width: 1.6rem; height: 1.6rem; animation-delay: 1.7s; }
  .sticker--glitter-5      { top: 25%;     left: 6rem;   width: 1.4rem; height: 1.4rem; animation-delay: 2.4s; }

  .tape { position: absolute; width: 70px; height: 26px; background: rgba(255,220,240,0.55); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); z-index: 5; backdrop-filter: blur(2px); }
  .tape--tl { top: -8px; left: 60px; transform: rotate(-8deg); }
  .tape--tr { top: -8px; right: 60px; transform: rotate(6deg); }

  .diary-page {
    position: relative; max-width: 780px; width: 100%; z-index: 3;
    background-color: var(--pink-paper);
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,105,180,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,105,180,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 28px 28px;
    border-radius: 4px 4px 2px 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 0 12px 40px rgba(255,20,147,0.15), 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.25), inset 0 0 60px rgba(255,182,193,0.12);
    transform: rotate(-1.2deg);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
  }
  .diary-page:hover { transform: rotate(-0.4deg) scale(1.005); }
  .diary-page::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 52px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: rgba(255,100,150,0.35); z-index: 1; }
  .diary-page::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -6px; left: -4px; right: -4px; height: 14px;
    background: var(--pink-paper);
    clip-path: polygon(0% 100%, 1% 20%, 2.5% 80%, 4% 10%, 5.5% 70%, 7% 5%, 8.5% 85%, 10% 15%, 12% 75%, 14% 0%, 16% 90%, 18% 20%, 20% 60%, 22% 5%, 24% 80%, 26% 30%, 28% 95%, 30% 10%, 32% 70%, 34% 0%, 36% 85%, 38% 25%, 40% 65%, 42% 5%, 44% 75%, 46% 20%, 48% 90%, 50% 10%, 52% 80%, 54% 15%, 56% 70%, 58% 0%, 60% 88%, 62% 22%, 64% 78%, 66% 8%, 68% 92%, 70% 18%, 72% 68%, 74% 3%, 76% 82%, 78% 28%, 80% 60%, 82% 0%, 84% 85%, 86% 20%, 88% 72%, 90% 8%, 92% 78%, 94% 28%, 96% 88%, 98% 12%, 100% 65%, 100% 100%);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 -2px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)); z-index: 2;
  }

  .diary-header { padding: 2rem 2rem 0.5rem 4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .diary-date   { font-family: var(--font-diary); font-size: clamp(0.65rem,1.5vw,0.8rem); color: var(--ink-blue); opacity: 0.7; }
  .diary-doodles { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--pink-neon); letter-spacing: 0.4em; opacity: 0.6; }
  .diary-rule   { margin: 0.5rem 2rem 0.5rem 4rem; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,20,147,0.4) 15%, rgba(255,20,147,0.4) 85%, transparent); }

  .diary-body   { position: relative; padding: 1rem 2.5rem 2rem 4.5rem; }

  .margin-note { position: absolute; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; font-family: var(--font-margin); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--pink-neon); opacity: 0.75; transform: rotate(-90deg); transform-origin: center center; white-space: nowrap; }
  .margin-note--left  { left: -1.5rem; top: 40%; transform: rotate(-90deg) translateX(-50%); flex-direction: row; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .margin-note--right { right: -1rem; top: 50%; transform: rotate(90deg) translateX(-50%); flex-direction: row; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--blood-light); }
  .margin-arrow { font-size: 1rem; }
  .margin-star  { color: var(--pink-hot); }

  .diary-text { position: relative; }
  .diary-entry { font-family: var(--font-diary); font-size: clamp(0.82rem,1.8vw,1rem); line-height: 2.1; color: var(--ink-dark); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; position: relative; }
  .diary-entry--1 { transform: rotate( 0.3deg); }
  .diary-entry--2 { transform: rotate(-0.4deg); }
  .diary-entry--3 { transform: rotate( 0.5deg); }
  .diary-entry--4 { transform: rotate(-0.2deg); }
  .diary-entry--5 { transform: rotate( 0.4deg); }

  .diary-cap { float: left; font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 0.75; padding-right: 0.15rem; padding-top: 0.15rem; color: var(--pink-neon); font-family: var(--font-diary); text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 rgba(255,20,147,0.2); }
  .underline-pink { border-bottom: 3px solid var(--pink-neon); padding-bottom: 1px; }
  .highlight-pink { background: rgba(255,20,147,0.15); padding: 0 3px; border-radius: 3px; }
  .scribble-word  { text-decoration: line-through; text-decoration-color: var(--pink-hot); text-decoration-thickness: 2px; }
  .scribble-word--angry { text-decoration-color: var(--blood); text-decoration-thickness: 3px; color: var(--blood); font-weight: bold; }
  .sticker-inline { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,105,180,0.2), rgba(255,20,147,0.1)); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,105,180,0.5); border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem; font-size: 0.9em; }

  .diary-entry--horror { color: #2a0a0a; line-height: 2.2; }
  .horror-word { color: var(--blood); font-style: italic; position: relative; display: inline-block; }
  .horror-word::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -2px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--blood); opacity: 0.4; border-radius: 1px; }
  .text-horror { color: var(--blood); font-weight: bold; }
  .horror-divider { text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-diary); color: var(--blood); opacity: 0.5; margin: 0.75rem 0; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 0.5em; animation: horror-blink 4s ease-in-out infinite; }

  .glitch-text { position: relative; display: inline-block; color: var(--blood); font-family: var(--font-diary); animation: glitch-idle 6s infinite; }
  .glitch-text::before { content: attr(data-text); position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; color: var(--pink-neon); clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 40%, 0 40%); animation: glitch-top 6s infinite; opacity: 0; }
  .glitch-text::after  { content: attr(data-text); position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; color: var(--blood); clip-path: polygon(0 60%, 100% 60%, 100% 100%, 0 100%); animation: glitch-bottom 6s infinite; opacity: 0; }

  .stain { position: relative; display: inline-block; margin: 0.75rem 0; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
  .stain:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .stain:focus { outline: none; }
  .stain-hidden-msg { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--font-pixel); font-size: 0.4rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-dark); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; white-space: nowrap; z-index: 2; text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,20,147,0.8); }
  .stain:hover .stain-hidden-msg, .stain:focus .stain-hidden-msg { opacity: 1; animation: glitch-idle 1s infinite; }
  .stain--coffee { width: 90px; height: 55px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 45%, rgba(111,78,55,0.55) 0%, rgba(111,78,55,0.25) 45%, transparent 70%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 65% 55%, rgba(111,78,55,0.3) 0%, transparent 50%); border-radius: 50% 45% 55% 48% / 52% 48% 55% 45%; filter: blur(0.5px); transform: rotate(-8deg); }

  .diary-signature { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 0.3rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1rem; transform: rotate(-0.5deg); }
  .signature-name   { font-family: var(--font-diary); font-size: clamp(1rem,2vw,1.2rem); color: var(--ink-dark); }
  .signature-doodles { color: var(--pink-neon); font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 0.4em; opacity: 0.7; }

  .torn-edge--bottom { height: 20px; background: var(--pink-paper); clip-path: polygon(0% 0%, 1.5% 100%, 3% 20%, 5% 95%, 7% 10%, 9% 80%, 11% 5%, 13% 90%, 15% 0%, 17% 75%, 19% 15%, 21% 100%, 23% 5%, 25% 85%, 27% 0%, 29% 70%, 31% 20%, 33% 100%, 35% 10%, 37% 85%, 39% 0%, 41% 80%, 43% 25%, 45% 100%, 47% 5%, 49% 90%, 51% 0%, 53% 75%, 55% 20%, 57% 95%, 59% 10%, 61% 80%, 63% 0%, 65% 88%, 67% 15%, 69% 95%, 71% 0%, 73% 78%, 75% 12%, 77% 92%, 79% 0%, 81% 85%, 83% 20%, 85% 100%, 87% 8%, 89% 82%, 91% 0%, 93% 90%, 95% 18%, 97% 78%, 100% 0%, 100% 0%, 0% 0%); margin-top: 1rem; filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .diary-page    { transform: rotate(-0.6deg); }
    .diary-body    { padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .diary-header  { padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0.5rem 3rem; }
    .diary-rule    { margin-left: 3rem; }
    .margin-note   { display: none; }
    .sticker       { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .tape          { width: 50px; height: 20px; }
    .diary-entry   { font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 2; }
  }

  @keyframes sticker-float { 0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); } 33% { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(3deg); } 66% { transform: translateY(3px) rotate(-2deg); } }
  @keyframes horror-blink  { 0%,92%,100% { opacity: 1; } 95% { opacity: 0.2; } 97% { opacity: 1; } 98% { opacity: 0.1; } }
  @keyframes glitch-idle   { 0%,88%,100% { transform: translate(0); } 90% { transform: translate(-2px,1px); filter: hue-rotate(80deg); } 92% { transform: translate(2px,-1px); } 94% { transform: translate(0); } 96% { transform: translate(-1px,1px); filter: hue-rotate(-40deg); } 98% { transform: translate(0); } }
  @keyframes glitch-top    { 0%,87%,100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(0); } 88% { opacity: 0.85; transform: translate(-3px,-1px); } 90% { opacity: 0.85; transform: translate(3px,1px); } 92% { opacity: 0; } }
  @keyframes glitch-bottom { 0%,89%,100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(0); } 90% { opacity: 0.85; transform: translate(3px,2px); } 92% { opacity: 0.85; transform: translate(-3px,-1px); } 94% { opacity: 0; } }
</style>